d the Watson AI platform, and holds a vast portfolio of technology patents.", "Amazon is an American multinational e-commerce and cloud computing company founded by Jeff Bezos in 1994 and headquartered in Seattle, Washington. Its AWS cloud division is the largest public cloud infrastructure provider worldwide."], "scores": [0.7966997617945911, 0.6490799611445625, 0.6402858712743937, 0.6269992148146525, 0.620053420523313], "model_name": "bge-base", "document_ids": ["Microsoft", "Oracle", "Google", "IBM", "Amazon"]}}